The firewalls protect the network, by filtering data allowed throough the network

SSL certificate is to allow for HTTPS decryption to HTTP and viceversa

the 3 clients, are to monitor the server data, collect the data generated

Server QPS can be monitored using Open Source tools eg Nagios, Cacti, Munin
    -Using commercial products eg SolarWinds, Datadog and New Relic

